cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this dataset or pipeline, please cite it."
title: "Hidden Health Data: AI-extracted open datasets from buried public-health documents"
abstract: >-
  An open-source pipeline that uses LLM-based structured extraction to convert
  buried public-health and healthcare documents (PDFs) into tidy, provenance-
  stamped, research-ready datasets. First release: Medicaid External Quality
  Review (EQR) technical reports.
type: software
authors:
